{"tid":1896814,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(2020DSE)中國文學討論區","createTime":"2020-02-25T10:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T13:33:39.000Z","uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"604bdf320ed5698533df7274f7687804b78dad5c","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚冷門嘅科都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c887f532d74c33801a8d84f7f65c198654a23daa","tid":1896814,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"又關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083c55e3be1ae20b6a2e14f595873abf7122b021","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"2019年報考中國文學科的考生只有1,650人，佔中學文憑試全體考生僅約2.9%，即是說，每一百名考生中，只有三人報考。當然，中國文學向來不是熱門科目，但在2010年會考，報考該科的考生尚佔總考生的6.8%，相較現時仍高出3.9個百分點。至於中國語文科，現時中文科四卷考試操練繁重，扼殺學生的課時、閒餘時間，根本無暇閱讀課外讀物，遑論體味文學之美。<br />\n<br />\n哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c92d084b6707119c328e2a331727071c9500b95","tid":1896814,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n應該會易合格的"},{"pid":"535bf642e0db86f32164aa7d080db0e76470e054","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c887f532d74c33801a8d84f7f65c198654a23daa","tid":1896814,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"又關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"就快考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89a161162dae04589203b2da6304c57ace891d4","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYC4ugZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYC4ugZ.png&h=b2fd5ae3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔會翻炒掛"},{"pid":"87cd4e2a75cef1d36f00daa562be68fb9894fcc6","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"有無貼題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350c29fa1d203cd5d2c9f5a07b042116288341dc","tid":1896814,"uid":184356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87cd4e2a75cef1d36f00daa562be68fb9894fcc6","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"有無貼題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"日出！<br />\n咁多年都冇考過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f7e1fbc932b833641a5318f0c8216f5b04ea30","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350c29fa1d203cd5d2c9f5a07b042116288341dc","tid":1896814,"uid":184356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87cd4e2a75cef1d36f00daa562be68fb9894fcc6","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"有無貼題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"日出！<br />\n咁多年都冇考過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"考過會唔會翻炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1 秦風‧蒹葭 (詩 經)<br />\n2 九章‧涉江 (楚 辭)<br />\n3 齊桓晉文之事章 (孟 子) (由「齊宣王問曰:&ldquo;齊桓、晉文之事，可得聞乎?」至「物皆然，心爲甚。王請度 之。」)<br />\n4 庖丁解牛 (莊 子)<br />\n5 蘇秦約縱 (戰國策) (節選自《秦策》，由「說秦王書十上」至「蓋可以忽乎哉」)<br />\n6鴻門會 (史記) (節選自《史記.項羽本紀》，由「沛公旦日從百餘騎來見項王」<br />\n至「沛公至軍，立誅殺曹無傷」) 7戰城南 (佚名)<br />\n8短歌行 (曹操)<br />\n9 歸去來辭(並序) (陶 潛) 10將進酒 (李白)<br />\n11登高 (杜甫)<br />\n12進學解 (韓愈)<br />\n13 醉翁亭記 (歐陽修)<br />\n14 前赤壁賦 (蘇 軾)<br />\n15 齊天樂(綠蕪凋盡臺城路) (周邦彥) 16 南鄉子(何處望神州) (辛棄疾)<br />\n17 雙調‧夜行船 秋思 (馬致遠)<br />\n18 法場(《竇娥冤》第三折) (關漢卿) 19 西湖七月半 (張 岱)<br />\n20 卻奩(《桃花扇》第七齣) (孔尚任) 21 接外孫賈母惜孤女 (曹雪芹)<br />\n2<br />\n<br />\n(節選自《紅樓夢》第三回，由「且說黛玉自那日棄舟登岸時」至 「也就不生別論」)<br />\n22 死水 (聞一多)<br />\n23 錯誤 (鄭愁予)<br />\n24 書 (梁實秋)<br />\n25 我的四個假想敵 (余光中)<br />\n26藥 (魯迅)<br />\n27碗 (西西)<br />\n28 日出 (曹禺)<br />\n(節選自第 2 幕，由「李石清由中們進」至「福升把黃省三拖下去」)"},{"pid":"475c768119e7263193336c35f84092a47c9b86d9","tid":1896814,"uid":303609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c92d084b6707119c328e2a331727071c9500b95","tid":1896814,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n應該會易合格的"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"易合格，難高分<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申5**</span>"},{"pid":"dfd75520721711571ee18dcb80998f4e438c1796","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"475c768119e7263193336c35f84092a47c9b86d9","tid":1896814,"uid":303609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c92d084b6707119c328e2a331727071c9500b95","tid":1896814,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n應該會易合格的"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"易合格，難高分<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申5**</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:20:18.000Z","msg":"點做到"},{"pid":"00c4ff4a801ada8770fa2fee1d80bbe6777dccf4","tid":1896814,"uid":303609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfd75520721711571ee18dcb80998f4e438c1796","tid":1896814,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"475c768119e7263193336c35f84092a47c9b86d9","tid":1896814,"uid":303609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c92d084b6707119c328e2a331727071c9500b95","tid":1896814,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n應該會易合格的"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"易合格，